{"tid":702653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"御理：本民青當年有食熱狗　梁天琦默許","createTime":"2018-06-15T05:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T13:05:13.000Z","uid":187729,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa66720eb470aa60be18b6777f1bb81c41c894a","tid":702653,"uid":187729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/133345_37c3cbf17fbfd5647d690fed1fb4aad6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F133345_37c3cbf17fbfd5647d690fed1fb4aad6.png&h=633f02b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/702144/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/702144/page/6</a><br />\n<br />\n見到御理呢隻熱普城玩具，水泥隊元老<br />\n<br />\n就知咩叫&quot;一日熱普城　一世熱普城&quot;<br />\n<br />\n到依家仲係活喺幻想<br />\n<br />\n熱狗冇錯、陳雲冇錯、黃毓民冇錯，千錯萬錯都係本民青梁游梁天琦錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccf7452306227482968fb752a2462aa32dbaa40","tid":702653,"uid":34884,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"熱狗同陳雲錯都錯喺選舉之後私怨上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔等於可以抹去選舉前被本民青同飯民狗瘋狂抹黑既事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026766e37f714bc75d1caf6d68e4e76a2999bd9d","tid":702653,"uid":69568,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"隻水泥隊肥閪幾時pk死"},{"pid":"1ba0eda7f9f7e619518124997a9d4ad7a8a3b2f2","tid":702653,"uid":34884,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"同埋我唔撚似熱狗咁，依家仲對梁天琦窮追猛打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而熱狗收左皮成年仲有班人喺到日日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi